headline: Q4 Earnings Outperformers: Patterson Companies (NASDAQ:PDCO) And The Rest Of The Healthcare Distribution & Related Services Stocks
summary: As the craze of earnings season draws to a close, here’s a look back at some of the most exciting (and some less so) results from Q4. Today, we are looking at healthcare distribution & related services stocks, starting with Patterson Companies (NASDAQ:PDCO).
